To launch software copy (Ctrl+c) the corresponding command and paste it in the command line (Ctrl+Shift+v):

McStas: 
mcgui

FullProf:
/opt/FullProf/winplotr-2006

Mantid:
mantidworkbench

Copy your data files to the desktop by pasting the following line on the command line:
cp -r /home/shared/FullProf_Data/ .
cp -r /home/shared/Additional_Data/ .
cp -r /home/shared/QENS_tutorial/ .
cp -r /home/shared/'Mark Analysis'/ .
